Some embodiments of the reports may show, for a given time period:



    

Brand and Model Outflow (what vehicles owners purchased when they returned to market, by brand and model);

Brand and Model Inflow (what vehicles buyers owned at the time of purchase, by brand and model);

Manufacturer and Brand Outflow (what vehicle owners purchased when they returned to market, by manufacturer and brand);

Manufacturer and Brand Outflow (what vehicle buyers owned at the time of purchase, by manufacturer and brand);

Segment Outflow (what vehicle owners purchased when they returned to market, by segment);

Segment Inflow (what vehicle buyers owned at time of purchase, by segment).

